="mailto:tkeane@swin.edu.au">tkeane@swin.edu.au</a>)</li>\r\n	<li><span style="color: #333399;"><strong>Sydney</strong>:</span> Fred Westling (<a href="mailto:fred@firstaustralia.org">fred@firstaustralia.org</a>)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Start a FLL Team', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '146-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-10-07 07:52:30', '2015-10-07 07:52:30', '', 146, 'http://localhost/firstau/2015/10/07/146-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
